          "description": "Very professional and friendly team. I've been scarred emotionally by soviet and then US military dentistry, and this team made me feel comfortable and safe again. They will work with you and explain what to expect. Highly recommend them. They have two offices so they work with what ever your schedule looks like. I have been going to them since 2016,  they even did an emergency root canal in 2020. Thank you!",
