          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSCyjDwv6gSKroXVic4wotprYp3AF0VNTT0cr5McZKq554uXF7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I can't say enough good things about Dr. Andrew Flores and his team. I was traveling from out of state (Tennessee) when I had a dental emergency \u2013 the crown on my front tooth came off on a Saturday! I was in a complete panic, but the staff was incredibly helpful and accommodating from the moment I called. They were able to get me in quickly, which was a huge relief.\n\nDr. Flores was fantastic. He was so kind, honest, and informative, explaining everything clearly. He took care of my tooth efficiently and professionally. What impressed me most was that he didn't take advantage of my situation. Being a traveler in a dental emergency is a vulnerable position, but Dr. Flores was fair and focused purely on providing excellent care. If I lived locally, he would absolutely be my regular dentist. I highly recommend this practice to anyone!",
